 patches. This result makes the\nGEV based approach potentially also interesting for cluster surveys with a\nsmaller area.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 Jan 2012 15:14:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 28 Mar 2012 09:25:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-03"}
